title: G-Fan Magazine Special collection #1 Very Rare
description:
This special edition reprints issues 1-8 of G-Fan, which were just Mimeographed newsletters when it started out.  Now the Magazine has a subscription of well over 10,000 readers and is the ONLY Magazine worth reading for Godzilla and all things Daikaiju or tokusatsu


seed for all to enjoy 

and watch for more scanned copies of G-Fan from me!  I love to spread the world of Godzilla to all!
